sellerCard.description:
I'm Alawo Ud Din, a web developer with over 5 years of experience. I love creating awesome web applications using PHP Laravel. 

I'm skilled in PHP, Laravel, HTML5, Bootstrap, API, WordPress development, JS and AJAX . I stay updated with the latest tech trends to deliver top-notch solutions that exceed expectations. I completed a variety of projects for the global clientele. Let's do yours.

description.content:
In the ever-evolving digital landscape, the role of a skilled PHP Laravel developer is paramount. That is why I am here.


With a 5 years of experience, I offer valuable expertise to fulfill your requirements. Choose me as your PHP developer, and rest assured that I'll utilize Laravel to create customized, impressive PHP websites perfectly tailored to your specific needs.


Provided services:


1. Twilio for SMS integration

2. Bug fixing and debugging in PHP laravel

3. Laravel website development from scratch

4. Admin Panel installation in laravel

5. CMS Development

6. Frontend Designing using Figma or PSD

7. Business website development using laravel

8. SaaS website development


My Skills:


  • C-panel
  • Rest API
  • HTML
  • Ajax
  • SQL/Database
  • CSS
  • JavaScript
  • PHP
  • Laravel
  • Bootstrap


Why choose me?

  • Timely delivery of project
  • If there is any bug, I will fix it even after the delivery
  • Daily work updates


Let's make your project idea much better than you imagined.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Which admin packages are you proficient in within the Laravel framework?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I am well-versed in several admin packages, including Voyager, Crudbooster, LaraAdmin, and Josh, which can be tailored to your project's unique needs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is the cost of a custom website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The price depends on project requirements. Contact me so I can provide a detailed quote according to your project.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I have a look at your previous work and portfolio?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Please feel free to contact me directly, and I will share my portfolio with you, showcasing my expertise and previous projects, except confidential ones.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you optimize websites for user experience and SEO?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, your website will have an SEO-friendly and user-friendly foundation. Contact me before placing the order.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you assist with WordPress installation, migration, and domain setup/configuration?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can, and the good news is that it is available at no additional cost. I can also set up and configure domains on Cpanel or VPS platforms.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer assistance and troubleshooting for Laravel or PHP-related issues?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I provide hands-on assistance through screen sharing for debugging and resolving issues related to Laravel and PHP development.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if there's something I need that is not included in your package or mentioned in the description?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: If there's a specific requirement not covered in my package or described in the details, feel free to reach out! I'm open to discussing customized solutions to accommodate your unique needs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is there anything you require that is not mentioned in my package and description?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: If there is something specific you need for your project that is not included in the package or mentioned in the description, feel free to let me know.

The final result was flawless, and I couldn’t be happier with his work. If you’re looking for a highly skilled and reliable programmer, I highly recommend Alawo Ud Din. I will definitely be working with him again in the future!
